#. type: Plain text
#: original_texis/frames.texi:217
msgid ""
"Emacs can also support horizontal scrolling if your mouse's wheel can be "
"tilted.  This feature is off by default; the variable "
"@code{mouse-wheel-tilt-scroll} turns it on.  If you'd like to reverse the "
"direction of horizontal scrolling, customize the variable "
"@code{mouse-wheel-flip-direction} to a non-@code{nil} value."
msgstr ""

